            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-10-17T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1947-05-04T18:00:00-05:00" n="509" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d509">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On February 2, 1948 a Treaty of Friendship, Commerce and Navigation between the
                    United States of America and the Italian Republic was signed in Rome. For the
                    text of the treaty and exchanges of notes see Treaties and Other International
                    Acts Series 1965 (63 Stat. (pt. 2) 2255). Documentation on the negotiations in
                    1947 and 1948 leading to the treaty is found in file 611.6531.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
